The '''Body Golem''' is one of the [[Golem (Ruins of Camdozaal)|golems]] found in the [[Ruins of Camdozaal]]. It can be found by awakening the rubble lying in the section north-east of the bank chest.

When you walk away from an awakened golem without killing it, it will disintegrate as if it died, without dropping any loot.

Body golems are notable for dropping the [[Barronite guard]], needed for construction of the [[Barronite mace]], and for dropping [[Body core|Body cores]], used in [[Runecraft]].

